[I] View disk usage

[T] KDiskFree displays the available file devices (hard drive partitions,
[T] floppy and CD drives, etc.) along with information on their capacity, free
[T] space, type and mount point. It also allows you to mount and unmount drives
[T] and view them in a file manager.

[U] https://apps.kde.org/kdf/

[A] The KDE-Team
